  <brief_title>Technical Optimization of Detection of KRAS, BRAF and NRAS Mutations on Tumor DNA Circulating in Metastatic Colorectal Cancer</brief_title>
  <acronym>CircuLOR-1</acronym>
  <official_title>Prospective Study of Technical Optimization of the Detection of KRAS Mutations, BRAF and NRAS by Next Generation Sequencing on Tumor DNA Circulating in Metastatic Colorectal Cancer.</official_title>
