  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study is to optimize the search by next-generation sequencing (NGS)
      mutations in the KRAS, BRAF and NRAS on circulating tumor DNA and compare the genetic
      profiles obtained with those from tumors embedded in paraffin
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
